0010 REM "CSM - Product ID Maintenance (Description)"
0020 REM "Program CSM.AB"
0022 REM "+-----------------------------------------------------------+"
0024 REM "| ADD+ON Software, Inc. Advantage/V Version 6.0.0 - 15May96 |"
